      </indexterm>Rescan Privileges</title>
    <para>The Rescan Privileges utility enables a user to realize
    newly-granted privileges without having to log out and log back in to the
    application. To realize newly-granted privileges, simply select the
    "Rescan Privileges" option to execute the utility. The privileges for the
    current user will be rescanned and updatedâ€”without the user having to log
    out of the application.</para>
  </section>
