  <section id="systemCheckForUpdates">
    <title>Check for Updates</title>
    <para>This option is available to system administrators and/or any users
    who have the privilege to create new users. When you select this option,
    the system will scan your xTuple system configuration and tell you if any
    updates are available for you to download. The feature does not perform
    the updates for you. Instead, it simply identifies updates that may be
    available to you.</para>
  </section>
