  <section id="systemExiting">
    <title><indexterm significance="normal">
        <primary>exiting</primary>
        <secondary>how to</secondary>
      </indexterm>Exit xTuple ERP</title>
    <para>There are two ways to successfully exit the system. Either use the
    "X" symbol associated with the desktop window. Or use the System menu's
    "Exit xTuple ERP" option. Both work the same way and are equally valid
    methods for exiting the application.</para>
    <para>After selecting this option, the application will close, returning
    you to your computer desktop.</para>
    <tip>
      <para>Be sure to close all open screens before exiting the system to
      help prevent data loss.</para>
    </tip>
  </section>
